Text:
Game works fine.
If you have W7 or vista you can get some color problems but if you install the patch to correct that problem the game wonâ€™t work. 
But the solution is simple. The color error occurs because some incompatibility with W7 explorer.exe . If you close se explorer before running the game you wonâ€™t have any problems. But it is kind of annoying doing that all the time you want to play. In order to do that automatically do the following:
1- Create a text document in Notepad
2- In that the document. txt paste the following information:
--------------------------------------------------------

@echo off
@echo ================================================
@echo WA Colour Fix! v1.00
@echo ================================================
@echo Simply place this BAT file into your Worms armageddon folder and execute it,
@echo this will close all instances of Explorer.exe then start the game, when closing
@echo the game, Explorer.exe is reloaded.

@echo off
taskkill /f /IM explorer.exe
WA.exe /nointro
Start explorer.exe
--------------------------------------------------------

3- Save the file, changing the extension â€œ .txt â€ to â€œ .bat â€œ (example Worms.bat)
8- Go to the folder where you installed the game and paste there  the file you created (Worms.bat)
9- Make sure that the executable file to run the game is named WA.exe (yes in uppercase letters)
10- Make a desktop shortcut for â€œworms.batâ€ and there you go. The game will close explorer.exe automatically before start and open it again when you close. No more problems  :D
